      <title>以色列准备应对伊朗袭击，油价升至十月高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/oil-shoots-to-6-month-high-as-middle-east-conflict-escalates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于以色列准备应对伊朗可能发动的袭击，石油价格跃升至十月份以来的最高水平，这一事态发展将威胁到占世界原油产量三分之一的地区的重大破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/oil-shoots-to-6-month-high-as-middle-east-conflict-escalates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 13:41:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
