      <title>随着短缺担忧加剧，罗布斯塔咖啡创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/robusta-coffee-hits-fresh-record-high-as-shortage-fears-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心产量下降将加剧咖啡豆短缺，罗布斯塔咖啡在伦敦创下新纪录。阿拉比卡品种也因基金买盘强劲而上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/robusta-coffee-hits-fresh-record-high-as-shortage-fears-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:15:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴货币因规避风险而跌至三个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/emerging-market-currencies-hit-two-month-low-on-flight-from-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币跌至近三个月来的最低水平，股市抹去了本周的涨幅，原因是美国利率前景发生转变，地缘政治紧张局势加剧引发了避险情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/emerging-market-currencies-hit-two-month-low-on-flight-from-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:42:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
